Name: Aiball
About the game: Please welcome Aiball. Actually, a lot of them. They're from a parallel universe. They are like us. They like to play football, run obstacle courses, compete in wrestling, or even make a mortal battle with the help of different weapons. By the way, some of them work part time as drunken porters. Try to live in their shoes and feel the hardships harsh life of Aiball. We are planning to make several modes: running the obstacle course, wrestling, escape from kindergarten, a fight to the death, drunken porters.
